Package: cockpit-battery
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Annonymos Developer
Description: Cockpit Battery - A simple battery info web app for Cockpit
 Cockpit Battery is a lightweight web application that provides real-time
 information about your system's battery status. It integrates seamlessly
 with the Cockpit web console, allowing users to monitor battery health,
 charge levels, and estimated time remaining directly from their browser.
